How to make a RNtrack release

1. Run `svn up` and `svn st -q`
2. Copy everything except readme.1st and ChangeLog from
   trunk/devel/releases/ to the root directory of the
   working copy.
3. Copy ChangeLog from trunk/devel/releases/ to trunk/
4. Insert new ChangeLog entries under the template line in trunk/ChangeLog
   There should be one blank line after the entries.
5. Run `release` from the root directory of the working copy.
